synopsis.text: In a futuristic city called Cosplay City, a sinister villain named Dolmeck, the evil Lord of Darkness, arrives with an army of monsters. He plans to destroy the city and everything in it. The only one who can stop him is Honey Kisaragi, a secretary with a secret power - she can transform into Cutey Honey, a multi-transformational android superhero. As Cutey Honey, Honey is able to change into different powerful forms to battle Dolmeck's forces. However, Honey also faces a threat from her past enemy, Panther Zora. With the city and its people in grave danger, Cutey Honey must use all her skills, weapons, and special abilities to defeat the monsters and villains that seek to cause destruction. It's a high stakes battle between good and evil, with the future of Cosplay City hanging in the balance.
